'''= organisation focused on creating a network of pioneers looking to improve the world'''

URL: http://www.broedwerk.be/

=== Description===

"Broedwerk looks to connect pioneers looking to improve the world together in one network. By organising morning and evening meetings, as well as session and workshops, Broedwerk hopes to inspire people but also connect people with aims to improve the world. New idees and new contacts to help people realise their plans and aims, but also introduces people to others who are pursuing similar goals."

